metadata.description: Disappointment Frog is the hero that none of us want, but all of us need. He makes us stronger by tearing us down, brightening our future by showing us the darkness. My superpower is to tell people harsh truths about themselves that they need to hear but, do not want to accept. Your DisFrog is a ticket to MERCH, Play, and private Discord. The rules can be found at https://disfrog.com/ This is just the start and much more to come, happy hunting. If you won't do it for you, or for them, then do it for the Haters!!!!!!
